Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.49,0:00:20.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你有沒有事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.12,0:00:21.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有哪裡受傷了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.37,0:00:24.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有沒有哪裡覺得痛 同學
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.03,0:02:24.99,Title - blur - eng - b,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(748,880)\bord0\blur10\fad(695,695)}Somebody in the Rain
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.03,0:02:24.99,Title - eng - w,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\pos(748,880)\fad(695,695)}Somebody in the Rain
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.84,0:02:39.72,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來今年的夏天需要考慮一下各種活動了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.47,0:02:46.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,停不下來啊 雨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.65,0:02:55.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同學 喂 我說你 沒事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.74,0:03:01.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,附近有醫院 現在就和你一起去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.45,0:03:03.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只不過在躲避的時候摔的動作大了點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.75,0:03:11.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 你受傷了 還是去醫院看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.00,0:03:13.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是擦傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.63,0:03:14.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.09,0:03:15.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是我的錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.67,0:03:19.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的 沒事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事 沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.27,0:03:31.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眼鏡我一定會賠償的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.02,0:03:34.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有其他事的話請聯繫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.75,0:03:56.29,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼 差點被車撞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.04,0:03:57.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.71,0:03:59.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說嗯…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.76,0:04:06.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,受傷了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.26,0:04:07.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.47,0:04:10.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼叫沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.85,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先把衣服脫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.56,0:04:16.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在幹什麼啊 快站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.27,0:04:18.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,把衣服脫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.23,0:04:19.44,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讓我看看傷勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.12,0:04:34.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,確實只是擦傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.96,0:04:36.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眼鏡怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,壞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.80,0:04:48.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 額頭上不是也有傷嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.31,0:04:51.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是留下傷痕要怎麼辦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:55.27,0:04:56.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之先用急救箱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.94,0:04:58.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.07,0:05:01.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小題大作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.53,0:05:05.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,小題大作？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.36,0:05:08.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這怎麼會是小題大作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.66,0:05:10.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無論是差點被車撞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.04,0:05:12.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還是只受了擦傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.04,0:05:14.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這都是因為運氣好而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.79,0:05:19.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那可是車子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.21,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是出了點差錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.55,0:05:25.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是會出人命的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.31,0:05:37.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.27,0:05:41.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你明白就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.65,0:05:46.53,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之先消毒 然後再纏上繃帶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.51,0:06:08.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.22,0:06:13.64,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也許會有些不方便 先忍耐一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.23,0:06:18.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有明天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.73,0:06:20.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暫且還是去一下醫院吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.52,0:06:22.19,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.98,0:06:23.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.53,0:06:24.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒大礙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.74,0:06:28.70,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.32,0:06:32.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在做飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,早安 長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.99,0:07:14.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天真早呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.16,0:07:16.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眼鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.29,0:07:18.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是備用的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.79,0:07:21.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因為之前的那個壞掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.84,0:07:26.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說的也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.97,0:07:40.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,晚上傷口是不是痛了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.77,0:07:46.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不讓我晚上住下來真的沒事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.07,0:07:48.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.57,0:07:51.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不用客氣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.65,0:07:53.74,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我和你都什麼關繫了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.92,0:08:13.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,被車撞了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是的不是的 是差點被撞了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.47,0:08:20.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在雨天視線不太好的地方想事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.64,0:08:22.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有注意到車
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.31,0:08:27.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然後呢 受傷了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.57,0:08:31.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是的 雖然到處都是擦傷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.69,0:08:32.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.28,0:08:36.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之沒發生大事太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.45,0:08:39.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.62,0:08:42.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了一臉陰沉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.08,0:08:49.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 雖然嘴上說沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是一直沒有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那當然是受到刺激了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.92,0:08:56.01,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,難得像今天那樣認真讀書
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:56.59,0:08:59.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,連玩遊戲的精力都沒有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.14,0:09:00.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.98,0:09:07.73,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,明明她受到驚嚇 心中惴惴不安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.56,0:09:11.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,而我卻總是斥責她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.53,0:09:13.57,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.57,0:09:15.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,冷靜點 朝倉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.91,0:09:19.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就因為我這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.91,0:09:23.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門有什麼想說的也說不出吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.62,0:09:26.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,確實你生氣起來很可怕呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,根本沒機會辯解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.00,0:09:35.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不會是說了什麼「禁止外出」之類的話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.80,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那個確實想到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.68,0:09:41.10,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是我還是沒有說喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有想過喔…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.10,0:09:47.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,過度保護也並不好喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.44,0:09:49.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.78,0:09:59.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.78,0:10:04.37,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的腦中完全沒有課程的記憶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.75,0:10:07.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這次考試範圍很大呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.67,0:10:09.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也沒自信呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.21,0:10:11.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂喂喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.21,0:10:14.38,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們還真是沮喪呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.84,0:10:17.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我把我珍藏的情報告訴你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.68,0:10:18.93,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,打起精神啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.43,0:10:21.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,珍藏的 呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.43,0:10:24.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼什麼 告訴我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.64,0:10:28.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,其實剛才從網球社那裡到得到消息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.35,0:10:32.52,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,車站前的sunkus有個很漂亮的女孩呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.69,0:10:34.65,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,又是女孩子的話題？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.19,0:10:38.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你還真是總能搞到這方面的情報呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.57,0:10:42.91,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說是搞到 還不如說我會吸引情報呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.49,0:10:44.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是幸福呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.08,0:10:45.87,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.33,0:10:50.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以啊 放學之後我們也抽點時間去看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.75,0:10:52.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也可以為考試鼓鼓勁呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.84,0:10:57.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 你在聽嗎 阿虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.34,0:11:00.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.01,0:11:01.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.55,0:11:03.55,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說谷口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.89,0:11:06.39,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你這次要到便利商店打網球啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.72,0:11:08.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼會變成那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:18.19,0:11:19.15,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,阿虛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.36,0:11:23.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,老師今天拜託了我一點事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你送長門回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.33,0:11:29.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要送到家喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.16,0:11:32.71,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 工作辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.54,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先走囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.96,0:11:40.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,拜拜 長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.05,0:11:41.26,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.80,0:11:46.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 那接下來…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 去社團活動室吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.10,0:12:35.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門 你在讀什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.11,0:12:43.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Le mys…me…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唉 不會念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.02,0:13:14.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.27,0:13:17.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,春日不在 還真是安靜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能安靜點也好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.58,0:14:16.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這種感覺就像回到了以前呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.46,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼也不做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.37,0:14:21.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們風格的文藝社
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.17,0:14:24.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接著你要讀什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.93,0:14:33.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,le pa pipi…pa…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,唉 完全不會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.87,0:14:54.03,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他們兩個還在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.09,0:15:07.84,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這麼說來長門 你換眼鏡了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.67,0:15:10.34,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,給人感覺氣氛不太一樣了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.14,0:15:12.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是為了改善一下心情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.18,0:15:17.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是備用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.72,0:15:19.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之前的昨天壞掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.81,0:15:20.89,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.56,0:15:25.77,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨天 真是糟呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.69,0:15:30.11,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你問了朝倉嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.74,0:15:31.86,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.70,0:15:34.16,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.95,0:15:36.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒受什麼傷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.70,0:15:39.50,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我聽說是沒什麼事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.75,0:15:47.30,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.67,0:15:51.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你在擔心我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:51.76,0:15:54.22,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼嘛 那是當然的啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.77,0:16:05.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼了 一直盯著我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.48,0:16:06.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.61,0:16:14.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.37,0:16:18.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.37,0:16:21.00,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,關心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.40,0:16:53.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.33,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.66,0:17:03.75,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我看那OK繃快掉下來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.21,0:17:07.58,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.42,0:17:13.88,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.05,0:17:15.63,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.09,0:17:18.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呃…那個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.60,0:17:25.23,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.36,0:17:29.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.82,0:17:31.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔…喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:33.61,0:17:35.24,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要去修眼鏡對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.74,0:17:36.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那樣的話我也要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.45,0:17:38.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有想要買的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.42,0:17:49.79,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\an8}謝謝惠顧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.88,0:17:53.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像要花很長時間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.80,0:17:57.18,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,鏡框都斷了也辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.68,0:18:02.68,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不過好像能修好真是太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.02,0:18:11.40,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門你沒問題嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.15,0:18:14.28,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,暫時要用那個了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.28,0:18:16.78,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,眼鏡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.95,0:18:19.82,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.32,0:18:22.95,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣啊 那就好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.83,0:18:26.12,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喔 鯛魚燒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.75,0:18:29.42,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要吃嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.83,0:18:31.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.34,0:18:32.92,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.27,0:18:51.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快要到夏日祭典了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.40,0:19:38.69,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天晚餐就在昨天的咖哩裡加入起司吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.24,0:19:40.90,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,長門喜歡這麼吃對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.54,0:19:57.59,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,味道怎麼樣 要再加點起司嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.30,0:19:58.96,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這樣就夠了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.05,0:20:00.76,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.06,0:20:12.94,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對了對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.06,0:20:17.07,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天的蘿蔔特賣 我買了很多喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.44,0:20:19.36,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這幾天我們做關東煮吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.99,0:20:24.20,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最近有點涼 夏天到來之前吃我覺得剛好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.62,0:20:27.41,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,朝倉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.99,0:20:30.45,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.75,0:20:32.25,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那邊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.08,0:20:38.09,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀 真抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.59,0:20:39.67,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒注意到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.51,0:20:49.47,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不快點吃的話菜要涼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.60,0:20:55.27,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 非常好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.92,0:21:22.17,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這段時間還是不要洗澡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.84,0:21:23.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,傷口會痛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.84,0:21:25.05,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.30,0:21:26.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:27.26,0:21:31.35,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,昨天也說過了 晚上要是哪裡疼的話就叫我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.81,0:21:33.14,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我會馬上過去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:33.98,0:21:34.31,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:35.69,0:21:37.98,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再來就是暫時別往外…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.56,0:21:39.06,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,外面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:39.65,0:21:43.32,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊不 沒什麼 我會自重的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.82,0:21:49.49,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你 關心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.99,0:21:53.08,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,理所當然的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.35,0:22:10.97,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,果然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.47,0:22:15.02,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,還有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:18.94,0:22:19.56,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.69,0:22:21.48,Text,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是誰？
